{"tid":2377922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊：不信一國兩制倒不如移民 |","createTime":"2021-01-24T04:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T09:00:09.000Z","uid":117622,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"76989550aac7b3b09a718f57bc8b744017b44368","tid":2377922,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T04:51:04.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員、資深大律師湯家驊認為，目前坊間就修訂《逃犯條例》的建議，原則或技術上不可行，反映提出意見人士，不明白修訂《逃犯條例》的宗旨和原則，甚至誤解政府建議。他說，如果反對修例者，從根本不相信本港司法獨立和一國兩制，他們的關注就難以解決，亦沒有討論空間，認為有關人士倒不如移民。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20190507/0/1/84/%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E8%80%85%E5%A6%82%E6%A0%B9%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8D%E4%BF%A1%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6-%E5%80%92%E4%B8%8D%E5%A6%82%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91-10127124.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20190507%2F0%2F1%2F84%2F%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%25A9%258A-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25A6%2582%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2588%25B6-%25E5%2580%2592%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25A6%2582%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591-10127124.html&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TavkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=88fb1c2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20190507/0/1/84/%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E8%80%85%E5%A6%82%E6%A0%B9%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8D%E4%BF%A1%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6-%E5%80%92%E4%B8%8D%E5%A6%82%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91-10127124.html</a><br />\n<br />\n叫人移民算唔算犯國安？"},{"pid":"c3f44adb6ba182d63c49161969c26fae43004b32","tid":2377922,"uid":217049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T04:51:57.000Z","msg":"MPF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"